SECTION, THE OPERATION OF A FAMILY CHILD CARE HOME OR LARGE FAMILY CHILD
CARE HOME SHALL BE:
(I) CONSIDERED A RESIDENTIAL ACTIVITY; AND
(II) A PERMITTED ACTIVITY.
(3) A PROVISION IN THE ARTICLES OF INCORPORATION OR A
